// 
// A sales rep submits a discount request. Anything 20% or under is auto-approved
// right away. Anything over 20% goes to the CRO queue. The CRO sees the queue,
// clicks "draft AI summary" on a deal, and gets a one-paragraph recommendation
// with a risk score. Then approve or reject in one click.
// 
//   ┌──────────┐ POST /api/deals             ┌──────────┐
//   │   Rep    │ ──────────────────────────> │  Server  │
//   │  (form)  │ <──────────────────────────  │          │
//   └──────────┘   response                   └────┬─────┘
//                                                  │ save
//                                                  v
//   ┌──────────┐ GET /api/deals/pending      ┌─────────┐
//   │   CRO    │ <────────────────────────── │  Deals  │
//   │  (queue) │ POST /api/deals/draft       │  table  │
//   │          │ PATCH /api/deals/:id        └─────────┘
//   └────┬─────┘
//        │  draft button
//        v
//   ┌──────────┐ ask claude  ┌─────┐
//   │ Drafter  │ ──────────> │ AI  │
//   │  Agent   │ <────────── │     │
